      { q: 'How much is the Alibarbar Ingot in Australia?', a: 'The Alibarbar Ingot 9000 Puffs costs just $40 AUD at IGET Vapes Original — one of the most affordable disposable vapes available in Australia. With 9,000 puffs, that\'s just $0.0044 per puff.' },
      { q: 'Where can I buy Alibarbar vapes in Australia?', a: 'You can buy genuine Alibarbar Ingot 9000 vapes online at IGET Vapes Original with fast Australia-wide delivery. We stock all 33 Alibarbar flavours and ship to Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, Adelaide, and every other city with $30 flat-rate shipping.' },
    ],
    relatedLinks: [
      { text: 'All 33 Alibarbar Ingot Flavours Ranked', href: '/blog/alibarbar-ingot-all-33-flavours' },
      { text: 'Alibarbar Complete Guide', href: '/blog/alibarbar-vapes-complete-guide' },
      { text: 'Best Vapes Under $50', href: '/blog/best-vapes-under-50-dollars' },
    ],
    seoContent: '<p>The <strong>Alibarbar Ingot 9000 Puffs</strong> is the most compact and affordable vape in the Alibarbar range. With <strong>33 premium Alibarbar flavours</strong> — the widest selection of any Alibarbar device — the Ingot offers incredible variety at just $40. Popular <strong>Alibarbar flavours</strong> include Strawberry Watermelon, Grape Ice, Skittles, Cool Mint, Kiwi Pineapple, FTP, Ribena, and Mango Ice.</p><p>Weighing only <strong>50 grams</strong>, the Alibarbar Ingot is the lightest disposable vape we stock. It\'s perfect for pocket carry, nights out, or anyone who prefers a discreet, lightweight vaping device that doesn\'t sacrifice on flavour or longevity.</p><p>Buy Alibarbar Ingot vapes online at IGET Vapes Original with <strong>fast delivery across Australia</strong>. All 33 Alibarbar flavours in stock with same-day dispatch. We deliver to Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, Adelaide, Gold Coast, Canberra, Hobart, Darwin and all regional areas.</p>',
  },
  'alibarbar-ice-adjust': {
    title: 'Buy Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000 Puffs Online Australia — Adjustable Ice | IGET Vapes',
    description: 'Shop Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000 puffs with adjustable ice intensity in Australia. 15 Alibarbar flavours, twist-dial airflow control, 20ml capacity. From $50. Fast Australia-wide delivery.',
    h1: 'Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000 Puffs',
    h1Accent: 'Adjustable Ice Intensity — Your Vape, Your Way',
