    highlights: [
      { icon: '💨', label: 'Puffs', value: '12,000' },
      { icon: '🧪', label: 'Capacity', value: '20 ml' },
      { icon: '❄️', label: 'Feature', value: 'Ice Adjust' },
      { icon: '🎨', label: 'Flavours', value: '15' },
    ],
    buyingGuide: 'The Alibarbar Ice Adjust is for vapers who want control over their menthol intensity. The twist ring at the base adjusts airflow continuously — clockwise for more ice, counter-clockwise for less. At $50 for 12,000 puffs, it\'s excellent value. Best sellers: Watermelon, Blueberry Blast, Mango Magic, and Strawberry Kiwi.',
    features: [
      { title: 'Adjustable Ice Intensity', desc: 'The twist-dial airflow ring gives you full control — dial up for an intense icy blast or dial down for a warmer, milder draw.' },
      { title: '12,000 Puffs', desc: 'One of the highest puff counts in the Alibarbar range, matched with a generous 20ml e-liquid capacity.' },
      { title: '15 Curated Flavours', desc: 'Every flavour is designed to work beautifully with the ice adjustment system — from fruity to candy to menthol.' },
      { title: 'Real-Time Customisation', desc: 'Unlike fixed-intensity vapes, the Ice Adjust lets you change the cooling sensation mid-session — no need to commit to one setting.' },
    ],
    faqs: [
      { q: 'How does the Alibarbar Ice Adjust work?', a: 'The Alibarbar Ice Adjust has a twist-dial ring at the base of the device. Turning it clockwise increases the menthol/ice intensity, while turning counter-clockwise reduces it. The adjustment is continuous — you can set any level from minimal cooling to maximum ice blast.' },
      { q: 'Does adjusting ice affect nicotine strength?', a: 'No. The ice adjustment only controls airflow and cooling sensation. Nicotine strength remains constant at 5% (50mg/ml) regardless of the ice intensity setting. It does not affect e-liquid consumption speed either.' },
      { q: 'How many puffs does the Alibarbar Ice Adjust have?', a: 'The Alibarbar Ice Adjust delivers up to 12,000 puffs from a 20ml e-liquid capacity. With the 650mAh rechargeable battery, you get the full 12,000 puffs over multiple charge cycles.' },
      { q: 'What are the best Alibarbar Ice Adjust flavours?', a: 'Top-selling Alibarbar Ice Adjust flavours include Watermelon, Blueberry Blast, Mango Magic, Strawberry Kiwi, Skittles, and Pineapple Coconut. The ice adjustment feature makes every flavour incredibly versatile.' },
      { q: 'How much is the Alibarbar Ice Adjust in Australia?', a: 'The Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000 Puffs costs $50 AUD at IGET Vapes Original. We ship to all Australian states with $30 flat-rate delivery — Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, Adelaide, and beyond.' },
    ],
